ode_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"<p>车程 750KM ，目前个人开过最长的单次才 100 多 KM ，无伴</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/901261","replies":124,"created_ts":1670552243,"created":"10:17:23","title":"这下放开了，过年回家准备自驾回去，但是没开过那么长的车程，有啥建议吗","author":"kevinfk2","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/kevinfk2","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0b6c2dee12f87046eb0ba6d4502251b6?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":901238,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1670445459","description":"<p>G304 还是 anywhere 。anywhere2s 和 3 对比如何，本人手 17.5</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/901238","replies":109,"created_ts":1670547220,"created":"08:53:40","title":"mac 无线鼠标推荐","author":"DigitalHarace","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/DigitalHarace","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cca8/a440/515252_mini.png?m=1606698612"},{"id":901398,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"<p>我一直未打疫苗，因为想等成熟的疫苗出来，后来病毒的毒性减弱后，也没动力打。但现在开放后想着要不要打。\n打的理由：\n目前开放后，感染率估计是指数性提升\n犹豫的理由：\n1 、目前国内都是灭活疫苗，我估摸着感染一次，和打一次疫苗的过程，是不是差不多？\n2 、国内新冠疫苗可能会有后遗症（这也是当初我等成熟疫苗的原因），国内媒体也不敢报，不清楚现在什么情况</p>\n<p>大家是什么打算？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/901398","replies":107,"created_ts":1670579119,"created":"17:45:19","title":"有未打新冠疫苗的 v 友吗？你打算打了吗？","author":"MrCsharp","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/MrCsharp","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6778790d1537961b63a7829b0aeabd65?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":901371,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>那个人去了中东，各种置顶多个渠道疯狂舔，就像之前的某冠军一样，这就是我大国风范？还是有点气节好吧，可以捧但这也太.........</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/901371","replies":78,"created_ts":1670573876,"created":"16:17:56","title":"媒体又开始疯狂舔了","author":"rusteer","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/rusteer","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ae89/1211/573733_mini.png?m=1654161478"},{"id":901226,"node":"分享发现","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1650127281","description":"<p>这个 Topic 的起源是有人觉得北京上海等这波依然是精准防控，只是回到年初政策。我就简单介绍下北京目前如何防疫的，大家可以自行判断：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>仅阳性及其同住人居家隔离，楼上楼下对门均不封控也不检测核酸。楼上阳了三天我才知道。不贴门磁不贴封条。</li>\n<li>基本不做流调不排查密接，会象征性的做几个装装门面。但周围阳的没有一个做了流调。</li>\n<li>十混一阳性凭疾控短信自行出门，注意是自行出门做核酸单管复核。</li>\n<li>不存在任何形式的临时封控。在对高风险区进行清零，一个单元阳了三四家还是低风险。</li>\n<li>抗原和核酸纯属自愿，不强制。只要不做核酸，当抗原阳性后，你可以继续上班和出门，除了堂食畅通无阻。你猜现在街上有多少感染者在活动？</li>\n</ol>\n<p>以抽样统计看，我猜北京应该有数十万阳性了。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/901226","replies":75,"created_ts":1670524590,"created":"02:36:30","title":"分享下北京防疫政策，看是精准防控还是躺平。","author":"swulling","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/swulling","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1ed3/f6c5/22404_mini.png?m=1340101995"},{"id":901284,"node":"OpenAI","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/openai","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fd2c/5e46/1135_mini.png?m=1670310953","description":"<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/sqcUflB.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sqcUflB.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ORj5cTU.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ORj5cTU.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/1W12AGj.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1W12AGj.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a>","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/901284","replies":60,"created_ts":1670555616,"created":"11:13:36","title":"ChatGPT 终于还是被玩坏了","author":"ISVStar","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ISVStar","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5a42/15ae/404475_mini.png?m=167055537